🥾 SHELL – Official Trailer (2025) | New Action Thriller Movie in 4K
When the road ends… the fight begins. Shell is the gritty new action thriller of 2025, where a lone driver takes on an unstoppable warlord to save what remains of a ravaged world.

🔎 Film Overview
In a post-collapse wasteland, Mara, a skilled truck driver, transports critical supplies across lawless territory. But when her convoy is ambushed by a ruthless gang led by the warlord known only as The Specter, she goes from surviving to fighting — in a high-speed chase where every mile pushes her to the edge.
